: "5", "bestRating": "5"}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": {"@type": "Person", "name": "David R."}, "datePublished": "2025-12-02", "reviewBody": "Java Burn 2.0 dissolves completely in my coffee without changing the taste. I've been using it for two months and feel more active throughout the day. Great addition to my routine.", "name": "Dissolves Perfectly in Coffee", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": "5", "bestRating": "5"}}, {"@type": "Review", "author": {"@type": "Person", "name": "Jennifer K."}, "datePublished": "2026-01-18", "reviewBody": "I was skeptical at first but decided to try Java Burn 2.0 with my daily coffee. I appreciate that it's made with natural ingredients and I feel more balanced energy without any jitters.", "name": "Natural Energy Without Jitters", "reviewRating": {"@type": "Rating", "ratingValue": "5", "bestRating": "5"}}]}, {"@context": "https://schema.org", "@type": "FAQPage", "mainEntity": [{"@type": "Question", "name": "What are the main ingredients in Java Burn 2.0?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Java Burn 2.0 contains 6 natural ingredients: Chlorogenic Acid (from green coffee beans), Camellia Sinensis (Green Tea), Chromium, L-Carnitine, L-Theanine, and a Vitamin Complex. Each ingredient is selected for its role in supporting metabolism, energy, and overall wellness when combined with coffee."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Is Java Burn 2.0 made with natural ingredients?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. Every ingredient in Java Burn 2.0 is entirely plant-based, Non-GMO, soy-free, and dairy-free. The formula contains no artificial fillers, preservatives, or synthetic additives."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "How does Java Burn 2.0 work with coffee?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Java Burn 2.0 is a tasteless powder designed to dissolve instantly in coffee. The 6 ingredients work synergistically with coffee's natural compounds to support metabolism, help maintain healthy blood sugar levels, and promote sustained energy throughout the day."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Does Java Burn 2.0 contain caffeine?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Java Burn 2.0 itself contains no added caffeine. It is designed to be mixed with your regular coffee, enhancing coffee's natural effects with metabolism-supporting nutrients."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Are Java Burn 2.0 ingredients backed by research?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Yes. Each ingredient is chosen based on established scientific understanding of its role in metabolism and wellness. Chlorogenic Acid, Green Tea catechins, Chromium, L-Carnitine, L-Theanine, and essential vitamins have all been widely studied for their effects on metabolic function, energy production, and overall health."}}, {"@type": "Question", "name": "Does Java Burn 2.0 contain any allergens?", "acceptedAnswer": {"@type": "Answer", "text": "Java Burn 2.0 is formulated without common allergens including soy, dairy, and gluten. It is entirely plant-based and Non-GMO. We recommend reviewing the full ingredient label and consulting your healthcare professional if you have specific allergy concerns."}}]}];
---
<Layout
  title={title}
  description={description}
  keywords={keywords}
  ogDescription={ogDescription}
  extraSchemas={extraSchemas}
>
  <main id="main">
      <section class="kw-hero">
        <div class="trimology-container">
          <div class="kw-hero-inner">
            <div class="kw-hero-text">
              <h1>Java Burn 2.0 Ingredients</h1>
              <p>Java Burn 2.0 contains six clinically studied nutrients designed to work synergistically with coffee for metabolism, energy, and weight management support.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="kw-hero-img">
              <img src="/assets/images/6-bottles.webp" alt="Java Burn 2.0 Ingredients" width="400" height="400" loading="lazy">
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    
      <section class="kw-section">
        <h2>Key Ingredients</h2>
    
        <h3>Chlorogenic Acid</h3>
        <p>A polyphenol found in coffee beans and green coffee extract. Research suggests it may help support metabolism and healthy blood sugar levels.</p>
    
        <h3>Green Tea Extract (Camellia Sinensis)</h3>
        <p>Rich in EGCG catechins, green tea extract has been widely studied for its effects on metabolism and fat oxidation.</p>
    
        <h3>Chromium</h3>
        <p>An essential trace mineral that may support healthy insulin sensitivity and carbohydrate metabolism.</p>
    
        <h3>L-Carnitine</h3>
        <p>Helps transport fatty acids into mitochondria where they can be used for energy production.</p>
    
        <h3>L-Theanine</h3>
        <p>An amino acid found in tea leaves that promotes calm focus and works synergistically with caffeine.</p>
    
        <h3>Vitamin Complex</h3>
        <p>Includes Vitamin D, B6, and B12 to support immune function, natural energy production, and overall metabolic health.</p>
    
        <div class="kw-quick-facts">
          <table>
            <tr><td>Formula Type</td><td>Proprietary blend of 6 nutrients</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Form</td><td>Tasteless powder packets</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Serving Size</td><td>1 packet per day</td></tr>
            <tr><td>Quality</td><td>Non-GMO, vegetarian, gluten-free</td></tr>
          </table>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
</Layout>
